description.en:
Sophia Lenish, the Baron&rsquo;s daughter, was eventually kicked out of her home after the Countess abandoned her engagement.

When I woke up in the forest where I was tired of walking, crying and sleeping, I had nowhere to go &hellip;

Did she have a sword at her throat!?

&ldquo;You should live by my side.&rdquo;

&ldquo;But I&hellip; will just be a burden.&rdquo;

This is the magic knight, Marquis Gilbert Forster, called &ldquo;Black Knight&rdquo; and Sophia was picked up by him.

A story of sweet and sweet love that takes back what you lost!
